uired by law."},{title:"Payments & Invoices",body:"All amounts shown are in Saudi Riyals and include VAT. The company may adjust subscription prices with at least 30 days advance notice. Fees paid for expired periods are non-refundable."},{title:"Service Provider Obligations",body:"The service provider is committed to delivering agreed services at high quality, adhering to specified working hours, not sharing customer data with any other party, and immediately reporting any issue affecting service delivery."},{title:"Service Termination",body:"Either party may terminate the agreement with 14 days advance notice. The company reserves the right to immediately suspend an account in case of violation of any of these terms or proven fraudulent practices."},{title:"Governing Law",body:"These terms and conditions are governed by the laws of Saudi Arabia. Saudi courts have jurisdiction over any dispute arising from the application of these terms, with competent courts located in Riyadh."}]},plans:{title:"Plans & Pricing",intro:"Choose the best plan for your laundry and unlock more features.",monthly:"Monthly",yearly:"Yearly",unlimited:"Lifetime",popular:"Most Popular",currency:"SAR",perMonth:"/ month",perYear:"/ year",empty:"No plans available right now",error:"Failed to load plans",retry:"Retry",free:"Free",feature:"Feature",featuresCount:"Includes {count} features"}},auth:{welcome:"Welcome!",tagline:"Log in and manage your customer services in Swivo \u2014 your personal guide to car washing delivered to your door!",login:"Log In",browseGuest:"Browse as Guest",invalidPhone:"Please enter a valid phone number",networkError:"Connection failed, check your internet and try again",otp:{title:"Verify Account",subtitle:"Please enter the verification code sent to your registered mailbox",next:"\u203a Next",resend:"Resend",resendIn:"Resend in",invalidCode:"Invalid verification code",attemptsRemaining:"Attempts remaining: {{count}}",lockedOut:"Too many attempts. Try again in {{second