th customers. As an independent biker, you are not an employee of Tamam and bear responsibility for the quality and safety of service delivery."},{title:"3. Earnings & Payments",body:"Your earnings are calculated at 90% of each completed order's value. Withdrawal requests are processed within two business days. Tamam reserves the right to adjust commission rates with prior notice."},{title:"4. Professional Obligations",body:"The biker must arrive on time, use appropriate equipment, protect customer property, and act professionally at all times."},{title:"5. Order Cancellations",body:"Cancellations are only permitted in exceptional cases. Repeated cancellations may affect your rating and could result in account suspension."},{title:"6. Privacy & Data Protection",body:"We are committed to protecting your personal data in accordance with our adopted privacy policy. Your data will not be shared with third parties except with your consent or as required by law."},{title:"7. Account Termination",body:"Tamam has the right to suspend or terminate your account in case of a violation of these terms. You have the right to close your account at any time by contacting technical support."}]}}},525,[]);
